OL,11,FDaniel Allen, 33, with an address at
OL,12,FMaghaberry prison but had been living
OL,13,Fwith the family in a remote cottage in
OL,14,FDerrylin.
OL,16,FHe admitted murdering 19-year-old
OL,17,FSabrina Gosset, Roman Gosset who was
OL,18,F16 and 15-month-old Morganna Quinn. He
OL,19,Falso admitted manslaughter of his
OL,20,Fpartner 45-year-old Denise Gosset by
OL,21,Fway of a suicide pact back in June.
