OL,6,FShe died from smoke inhalation.
OL,8,FDetective Inspector Hazel Miller said:
OL,9,F"Three generations ` a mother, her two
OL,10,Fchildren and her granddaughter `
OL,11,Fperished in a fire deliberately
OL,12,Fstarted by Daniel Allen in their home
OL,13,Fin Derrylin. This was on the morning
OL,14,Fof 27 February 2018.
OL,16,F"The four whose lives were lost were
OL,17,FDenise Gosset, aged 45, her 16-year
OL,18,Fold son Roman, her 19-year-old
OL,19,Fdaughter Sabrina, and Sabrina's baby
OL,20,Fdaughter Morgana. Morgana was just 15
OL,21,Fmonths old.
