OL,6,F"Allen pleaded guilty to the murder of
OL,7,FSabrina, Roman and Morgana. He denied
OL,8,Fthe murder of Denise but confessed to
OL,9,Fher manslaughter, and also admitted to
OL,10,Farson with intent to endanger life.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Miller continued:
OL,13,F"This was a horrific and cruel act.
OL,14,FIt's hard to even begin to imagine the
OL,15,Fpanic, fear and sheer suffering.
