OL,6,F"I'd like to acknowledge the efforts
OL,7,Fof our police officers and of
OL,8,Fcolleagues from the Fire Service and
OL,9,Fthe Ambulance Service, who attended
OL,10,Fthis heart-breaking scene and tried so
OL,11,Fhard to save the family. I'm also keen
OL,12,Fto thank neighbours and local people
OL,13,Ffor their selfless support.
OL,15,FShe added: "With the use of forensic
OL,16,Fevidence, and working in partnership
OL,17,Fwith the Public Prosecution Service,
OL,18,FDaniel Allen has today been held
OL,19,Faccountable for his actions.
